Question:
Is there a RH850/F1KM-S2 starter kit?
Answer:
No, there is no a starter kit specifically for RH850/F1KM-S2. F1KM-S4 starter kit works perfectly for the RH850/F1KM-S2 as well. It serves as a simple and easy to use platform for evaluating the features and performance of both F1KM-S4 and F1KM-S2.
Suitable Products
RH850/F1Kx
